Hello all fellow questers. <br>
<br>
First, these enraged goblins /con sometime yellow and usually red to a 12th warrior. So I think their actual level is 14 to 15 and maybe 16 (I can't think of a 8th goblin hitting me for 32!). <br>
<br>
Now the good news. This is part of the new(?)serie(?) of cleric quests. It is initiated by talking to Bronlor Lightblade in the warrior guild. Odd he isn't at least in the pally guild, but that is... He can be found in the room next to Byzar Bloodforge whom you turn regular beads and ogres'heads to. Hail him and say you are a priest of the great Brell Serilis (even if not true <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ). Go on with green rascals and that you will return the beads so he will give some other infos on the high caliber and fighting style of this gobs. Then head W-NW from x-road to the cul-de-sac valley. Spawn loc is ~neg300<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> os1000. You need 4 beads, they are three and spawn every 17mn. No loot but beads (drops everytime though). <br>
When you return the 4 beads you got the Symbol: <br>
<br>
=&gt; Lore NoDrop Brell-Serilis <br>
=&gt; Cleric(dwf-gnm) <br>
=&gt; Neck AC3 Wis+1 Mana+3 <br>
=&gt; Effect Strenghen <br>
<br>
I never got anything else. Faction changes are: <br>
+Clerics of the underfoot <br>
+King Kazon <br>
+Miner's guild 249 <br>
<br>
Bronlor ends his thanking by saying:&quot;Return to me when you are ready fer your next task&quot;. So I assume you can go on with the quest for a 2nd level Faith item, like others religious symbols. Never find what to say to follow though. I m kindly consider. Maybe you need higher reputation? <br>
Or it's not implemented yet? <br>
<br>
Not that good item for the level it require, but the next level symbol should be nice <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
Feel free to tell if you see me online <br>
<br>
Skinn Bleiz Yaouank <br>
27th season serving Tunare <br>
Ranger of the Faydark <br>
Ally of the stormguard <br>
<br>
PS: English is not my native language, so please be fair about it<br>
-------------------------------------------------------<br>
End Copy...<br>
